Package: stminsights
Type: Package
Title: A 'Shiny' Application for Inspecting Structural Topic Models
Version: 0.4.3
Date: 2024-06-21
Authors@R: c( person("Carsten", "Schwemmer", email =
        "c.schwem2er@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID =
        "0000-0001-9084-946X"), role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Jonne", "Guyt", email = "j.y.guyt@uva.nl", role =
        "ctb") )
URL: https://github.com/cschwem2er/stminsights
BugReports: https://github.com/cschwem2er/stminsights/issues
Description: This app enables interactive validation, interpretation
        and visualization of structural topic models from the 'stm'
        package by Roberts and others (2014) <doi:10.1111/ajps.12103>.
        It also includes helper functions for model diagnostics and
        extracting data from effect estimates.
Imports: stm (>= 1.3.7), tidygraph (>= 1.3.1), ggraph (>= 2.2.1),
        igraph (>= 2.0.3), ggrepel (>= 0.9.5), shiny (>= 1.8.1),
        shinyBS (>= 0.6.0), shinydashboard (>= 0.7.2), shinyjs (>=
        2.1.0), ggplot2 (>= 3.5.1), purrr (>= 1.0.2), stringr (>=
        1.5.1), dplyr (>= 1.1.4), tibble (>= 3.2.1), DT (>= 0.33.0),
        readr (>= 2.1.5), huge (>= 1.3.5), stats, scales
